  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个数据管道的流程图，从源数据文件开始，经过摄取、验证，最后到消费端。核心是要体现两层验证机制。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Source Dataset Files",
        "Raw Ingestion",
        "Raw Validation",
        "Processed Data Generation",
        "Processed Validation",
        "Analytics / ML Consumers"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了。第一层验证是Raw Validation，第二层是Processed Validation。那如果验证失败的话，流程应该怎么处理？是直接终止还是有降级方案？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "RAWVAL",
        "PROCVAL",
        "STOP",
        "SAFE"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "第一层失败必须直接终止Pipeline，这是安全底线。但第二层失败可以降级——我们叫Inference Suppressed，进入Fallback Mode，这样系统还能跑，只是不输出推理结果。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "STOP",
        "SAFE",
        "Inference Suppressed",
        "Fallback Mode"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "好的，所以Raw Validation有两个出口：PASS走向Processed Data Generation，FAIL走向Pipeline Halt。Processed Validation也有两个出口：VALID到Analytics/ML Consumers，INVALID到Inference Suppressed。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "RAWVAL",
        "PROCESS",
        "STOP",
        "PROCVAL",
        "CONSUME",
        "SAFE"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，就是这样。另外STOP和SAFE这两个节点需要视觉突出，STOP用红色系，SAFE用黄色系警告色。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "STOP",
        "SAFE",
        "style"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已经画好了主干流程：Source Dataset Files → Raw Ingestion → Raw Validation → 分支。两个终止节点也加上了样式，STOP是浅红填充深红边框，SAFE是浅黄填充深黄边框。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "SRC",
        "INGEST",
        "RAWVAL",
        "STOP",
        "SAFE"
