      "utterance": "已添加分支标签。现在从Raw Validation分出|PASS|到Processed Data Generation，|FAIL|到Pipeline Halt；Processed Validation分出|VALID|到Analytics/ML Consumers，|INVALID|到Inference Suppressed。",
